*Krivi* je čovek ubiče nevine. (The guilty man killed the innocent.)

*Krivim* se za svoje greške. (I am to blame for my mistakes.)

On je *kriv* za to što se desilo. (He is guilty for what happened.)

Oni su *krivili* jedni druge za neuspeh. (They blamed each other for the failure.)

*Krivo* je shvatanje da je to bila njegova greška. (It is wrong to think that it was his mistake.)

*Krivac* je uhapšen. (The culprit has been arrested.)